---
title: Venison & Beef Cottage Pie with Golden Cheddar Topping & Garden Salad
description: This cosy cottage pie packs a veggie-loaded beef base full of flavour, then gets topped off with decadent and delicious creamy mashed potatoes, plus a layer of melted Cheddar. Comforting, tasty, and filling, this nostalgic meal is checking off all the boxes!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/nz-cheesy-venison-beef-shepherds-pie-c9919135.jpg
